name: Jennifer Ngetich
body:
## Hi, I'm Jen. I'm a goofy Florida native who builds awesome websites.


### Long Story Short
I'm an engineer getting a fresh start in web development. Currently looking for an entry level position based in Greenville, SC. Check out my GitHub to see my open sourced projects, but know I've worked on some private internal apps as well :)

Technology Toolbox:
* Git and GitHub
* HTML
* HTML preprocessors (Slim)
* CSS3
* CSS preprocessors (Sass/Compass) 
* Responsive CSS / media queries Design fundamentals
* JavaScript
* jQuery
* Underscore.js
* Backbone.js
* JS testing
* CoffeeScript
* JavaScript templating
* Ruby 101
* Rails basics
* Heroku deployment with Git
* Parse as a backend
* Front end package managers, tools, asset loaders, and generators
* Photoshop 
* WordPress
